JRWebViewActivity.FinishReceiver Class Reference

Inherits BroadcastReceiver.

List of all members.

Detailed Description

Used to listen to "Finish" broadcast messages sent by JRUserInterfaceMaestro. A facility for iPhone-like ability to close this activity from the maestro class.
